name: v10.2.0
body:
## What's Changed
* Support async profiler feature by @zhengziyi0117 in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/101
* fix: async profiler send data dual stream by @zhengziyi0117 in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/102
* Add new protocols for browser performance data by @mrproliu in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/103
* Add alarm baseline protocol by @mrproliu in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/104
* Remove alarm baseline protocol by @mrproliu in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/105
* Add browser web interaction protocol support by @mrproliu in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/106
* Add host header in eBPF HTTP request by @mrproliu in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/107

## New Contributors
* @zhengziyi0117 made their first contribution in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/101

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/compare/v10.1.0...v10.2.0

name: v10.1.0
body:
## What's Changed
* Wrap the node info to metadata in the Access Log Protocol by @mrproliu in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/93
* Revert "Wrap the node info to metadata in the Access Log Protocol" by @wu-sheng in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/94
* Adding exclude namespace policy in the eBPF Access Log Protocol by @mrproliu in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/96
* fix import of command.proto by @wbpcode in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/98
* Adding attachment fields to describe the environment in eBPF ALS by @mrproliu in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/99
* Adding security policy in ztunnel environment by @mrproliu in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/100

## New Contributors
* @wbpcode made their first contribution in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/98

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/compare/v10.0.1...v10.1.0

## What's Changed
* Provide eBPF based Access Log Service by @mrproliu in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/88
* Fix compile eBPF access log failure by @mrproliu in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/89
* Enhance eBPF Access Log collecting data by @mrproliu in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/90
* Adding fields into access log protocol by @mrproliu in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/91
* Update protocol type in access log by @mrproliu in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/92


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/compare/v9.7.0...v10.0.0

## What's Changed
* Support collect ZGC memory pool metrics by @Z-Beatles in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/86
* Fix CI to run on the latest Ubuntu by @wu-sheng in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/87

## New Contributors
* @Z-Beatles made their first contribution in https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/pull/86

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/apache/skywalking-data-collect-protocol/compare/v9.5.0...v9.7.0
